      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Great opportunity to own a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 This car is in good condition \u2014 the exterior presents nicely with only minor signs of normal everyday use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it runs reliably and has been properly maintained, making it a solid choice for anyone looking for a trustworthy ride without the mint-condition price tag. A genuinely good car at a fair price \u2014 come take it for a spin!",
