    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition and represents a dependable, well-maintained used car purchase. The exterior presents nicely for its age \u2014 you'll find only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use, but no significant dents, rust, or structural damage. The paint retains good color and gloss overall. The interior is clean and comfortable, with seats showing modest wear but no major tears or damage; all controls, windows, and features function as expected. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no warning lights or known mechanical issues \u2014 it starts easily and drives confidently on the road. The tires have reasonable tread remaining, and the brakes feel responsive. This is a solid everyday driver that has been cared for and should continue to serve its next owner well without requiring immediate major repairs. Buyers can expect a vehicle that is ready to use, though as with any used car, routine maintenance should be kept up to date.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
