    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and that designation is fully warranted in every respect. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless \u2014 a deep, rich gloss that retains its showroom brilliance with zero scratches, chips, swirl marks, or paint imperfections of any kind. The body panels are perfectly aligned, and all trim, chrome, and glass are in pristine shape. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells as though it just rolled off the lot \u2014 the upholstery is spotless, the carpets are clean, and every surface is free of wear, staining, or damage. All electronic systems, controls, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. The tires have substantial tread remaining and show even wear. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health \u2014 no warning lights, no unusual noises, no deferred maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that truly requires nothing. A full inspection is welcomed and encouraged.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely transparent with all potential buyers. The car has significant wear and multiple issues that should be carefully considered before purchase. Mechanically, the vehicle has known problems that will likely require attention and repair work \u2014 it is not in a turn-key, worry-free state. The exterior and interior both show heavy signs of use, including noticeable body wear, fading, and interior deterioration. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project vehicle, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is prepared to invest in repairs. We are pricing this vehicle accordingly to reflect its current state honestly. Please inspect thoroughly before purchase and factor in potential repair costs.",
      "price": 5500.0,
